{"tid":584923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【蘋果照相機】正義柔情永在","createTime":"2018-03-08T08:08:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T08:08:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5e8059531004f71f7d6551e78133e6b9f50cabf3","tid":584923,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T08:08:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180308/20325932\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180308%2F20325932&d=XZKGZzH3RpoVKciqCDwveKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=1c8eb3b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180308%2F20325932&h=fa50a0e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180308/20325932</a><br />\n<br />\n【蘋果照相機】正義柔情永在<br />\n<br />\n頭條   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一張照片勝過千言萬語！<br />\n<br />\n攝影師每日以相機拍下千百萬張照片，將一些大家看似熟悉的東西，以用不同的觀點與角度，讓你重新細看。<br />\n<br />\n【蘋果照相機】為大家呈現新聞重要時刻，以細膩照片，分享鏡頭背後的甜酸苦樂。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果攝記fb： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/1OlyZxX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F1OlyZxX&d=XZKGZzH3RpoVKciqCDwveKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=feaac08c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/1OlyZxX</a><br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t適值兩會　炒人令林鄭及新地郭氏尷尬<br />\n頭條 6小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t面臨失業　單親媽無悔<br />\n頭條 6小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t羅致光早上拒評論　林鄭下午稱介入<br />\n頭條 6小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t鄭耀棠：九巴炒人觸動工會底線<br />\n頭條 6小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t九巴跪低暫准4車長復職　工會斥緩兵之計<br />\n頭條 6小時前"}]}